            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I just added a diffing step to the CI runs that compares the generated test C/C++ sources of the latest master to the current test run, both for master builds and PRs.\nhttps://github.com/cython/cython/commit/e82ed27f8b813f4883991fb0321ae98293c24f63\n\nLooking through one of the diffs shows a couple of random changes that seem worth eliminating.\n\n```patch\ndiff -r -udB -x '*.py*' -x '*.html' -x '*.so' TEST_TMP/run/c/unicode_identifiers/unicode_identifiers.c ../TEST_TMP/run/c/unicode_identifiers/unicode_identifiers.c\n--- TEST_TMP/run/c/unicode_identifiers/unicode_identifiers.c    2026-05-14 03:26:30.000000000 +0000\n+++ ../TEST_TMP/run/c/unicode_identifiers/unicode_identifiers.c 2026-05-14 04:19:59.336443416 +0000\n@@ -2895,7 +2895,7 @@\n-static PyObject *__pyx_ff_map_fused_f3fa2a_1_2_a49aa9__float__and_43f53f__19unicode_identifiers__dund__etc(PyObject *); /*proto*/\n+static PyObject *__pyx_ff_map_fused_a764de_1_2_a49aa9__float__and_43f53f__19unicode_identifiers__dund__etc(PyObject *); /*proto*/\n```\n\n```patch\ndiff -r -udB -x '*.py*' -x '*.html' -x '*.so' TEST_TMP/compile/distutils_libraries_T845/a.c ../TEST_TMP/compile/distutils_libraries_T845/a.c\n--- TEST_TMP/compile/distutils_libraries_T845/a.c       2026-05-14 03:20:22.000000000 +0000\n+++ ../TEST_TMP/compile/distutils_libraries_T845/a.c    2026-05-14 04:10:49.419104332 +0000\n@@ -4,8 +4,8 @@\n {\n     \"distutils\": {\n         \"libraries\": [\n-            \"lib_x\",\n-            \"lib_y\"\n+            \"lib_y\",\n+            \"lib_x\"\n         ],\n```\n\n```patch\ndiff -r -udB -x '*.py*' -x '*.html' -x '*.so' TEST_TMP/compile/c/profile_exttypereturn/profile_exttypereturn.c ../TEST_TMP/compile/c/profile_exttypereturn/profile_exttypereturn.c\n--- TEST_TMP/compile/c/profile_exttypereturn/profile_exttypereturn.c    2026-05-14 03:20:46.000000000 +0000\n+++ ../TEST_TMP/compile/c/profile_exttypereturn/profile_exttypereturn.c 2026-05-14 04:11:20.640917457 +0000\n@@ -4522,7 +4522,7 @@\n   /*--- Execution code ---*/\n-  __Pyx_TraceStartFunc(\"PyInit_profile_exttypereturn\", __pyx_f[0], 1, 1, 0, 0, __PYX_ERR(0, 1, __pyx_L1_error));\n+  __Pyx_TraceStartFunc(\"PyInit_profile_exttypereturn\", __pyx_f[0], 1, 2, 0, 0, __PYX_ERR(0, 1, __pyx_L1_error));\n```\n\nProbably just due to the test setup, but at least the long path seems unhelpful:\n```patch\ndiff -r -udB -x '*.py*' -x '*.html' -x '*.so' TEST_TMP/memoryview/memoryview_shared_utility/pkg2/CythonShared.c ../TEST_TMP/memoryview/memoryview_shared_utility/pkg2/CythonShared.c\n--- TEST_TMP/memoryview/memoryview_shared_utility/pkg2/CythonShared.c   2026-05-14 03:20:42.000000000 +0000\n+++ ../TEST_TMP/memoryview/memoryview_shared_utility/pkg2/CythonShared.c        2026-05-14 04:11:24.120309594 +0000\n@@ -1368,7 +1368,7 @@\n /* #### Code section: filename_table ### */\n \n static const char* const __pyx_f[] = {\n-  \"../../../../../../../../tmp/tmpmh5rgk6p/CythonShared.pyx\",\n+  \"../../../../../../../../tmp/tmpbcp7cle1/CythonShared.pyx\",\n   \"View.MemoryView\",\n };\n```\n",
            "created_at": "2026-05-14T05:49:17Z",
